data.name: label10.Text
data.value: This software has two modules in it. The Database Export and Database Cleanup. Database Export can be used to export any Microsoft SQL Server Database(s) to a MySQL Database(s). The schema of both database(s) need to be similiar. This export tool exports only the data to the MySQL Database. The source Database should be a Microsoft SQL Server database(s) and the destination database should be a MySQL database(s). Database Cleanup can be used to clear the data of any Microsoft SQL Server database or MySQL database. This has two options related to project eMax.
